Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.38,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:10.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:13.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Was that Komukai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:14.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Komukai speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:30.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:33.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,About that, please let me check it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:46.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes. \N-Give this to Department 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:49.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:50.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take some water, so I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:53.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:23.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:25.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sure. Do you mind that we have a yellow-colored dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:26.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yellow? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's my lucky color today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:29.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oyakodon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:30.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mass production-type...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:01:59.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:01.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The way that you're starting your love is a mass-production type.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:04.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you in a one-sided relationship, Riko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who is that person? From back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In the company? From an app?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:10.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In the company, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he in Department 3? Department 2? Or Department 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 1, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:16.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:17.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san huh? I see that you're going for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:22.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:23.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They just said "Love", didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:31.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Office romance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Could it be an affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:37.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Office romance is hard after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:39.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wonder who the person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, I'm going to teach her the basics...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to teach her all about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:44.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's power harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:52.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your clothes, hair, nails, your a bit expensive hand cream, fixing your make-up, lucky color,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and hanging around when you go pass Department 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:56.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's confirmed then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your feelings for him developed because of the Mini 4WD, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We can't help you out if you don't admit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please let us help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I did this after looking up various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:18.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Men does not look at our nails, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Does Oishi-san like this kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no data regarding that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There must be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's workaholic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He loves Mini 4WD and Sambomaster
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What kind of girls does he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By the way, he's single, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,First things first, we must learn about our enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,During competition too, the key of success is to know the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We have to learn everything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Big Stone Investigation HQ]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard Chihiro confessed to Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That receptionist confessed to Oishi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:06.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's also Maki-san from accounting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"Sharing a drink with my senior whom I respect."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"Sake relaxes both of our hearts."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:16.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"He also has his own past."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"Everyone lives while hiding those scars."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"In this big city of Tokyo."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"Asai Yuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's too much, Asai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That person is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san is a difficult person to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see, thank you for the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!, Google and Asai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Chihiro the receptionist and Maki from accounting, both of them confessed to Oishi-san.]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[He turned them down.]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Oishi-san is currently single.]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:07.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[He turned down all mixer invitations.] \N[Even though he's single, he turned down all invitations, what a serious person.]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:10.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Does that mean that work is more important than love for him?]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:15.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[It seems like 3 years ago he was dumped by his then girlfriend whom he dated for a long time.]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[He was quite sad at the time.]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did she got her heart broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's better than a prolonged and deep scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:38.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, I'm going to lend her my ear so she can complain as much as she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:39.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's power harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't even ask what my subordinate's troubles in this Reiwa era.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get trendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:54.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:55.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:12.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He turned down all mixer invitations even though he's single.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He got his heart broken 3 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you think that he still has feelings for his ex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is a big possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you have any information about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Her name is Kita Hinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:23.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She was Oishi-san's classmate in college,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,she is the only daughter of Kakitsubata, a {\i1}sake{\i0} brewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She opened a {\i1}sake{\i0} bar 3 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Didn't Oishi-san always drink {\i1}sake{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe that is because of his ex girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't see her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,First things first is know your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't learning about her scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's scary after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:00.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're going to the {\i1}sake{\i0} bar, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:05.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is for Riko-san's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't get too comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's great don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Analyze it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:20.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is she the owner of this bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:43.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look like she got many holes, not cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is great, it's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A well proportioned beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:53.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Impeccable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She is the type of person who looks down on others without realizing it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The sales of this {\i1}sake{\i0} is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's too perfect that she loses all interest in love or other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:01.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san is far from perfect, so I'm at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who's ally are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:06.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? \N-Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is your first time here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The Kaika is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My father and I made that {\i1}sake{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You sure are a good child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My senior at work, Oishi-san, told me about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Oishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,At first I thought that you were an annoying perfectionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:45.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Apology accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:50.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But if that were your personality, the world is bugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:54.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because I behave like this, people say that I'm a lonely or iron owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,but it's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that she's pretty, but she's actually cute, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san is a mysterious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Which part of him is mysterious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's just a normal man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's our company's ace, in other words, he's a Gundam employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:08.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:09.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's a workaholic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is super unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he a man that makes women cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:24.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In the end, he looks the best when he is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I also fell for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is your dream again, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:31.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Being a rich person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We won't lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Was that also part of your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:54.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't tell Oishi that I said hello, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:55.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What happened between us is in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:08.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He surprisingly has his flaws, but please continue to support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:10.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Another round please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to scout, but ended up drinking to much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The mummy catcher became a mummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:31.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Their relationship ended a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What was she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:42.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She was of medium height and had no distinctive features.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe Oishi-san is someone who does not have any preference when it comes to appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have any preference?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say, but... \N-Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:56.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As for her personality, she's a workaholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She loved her work more than Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:02.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's like an AI that lacks emotion... \N-Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Stop it, it's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:10.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, she's a really pretty person,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,but after I talked to her, I found that she was a really cute person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:17.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We became friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What a cute person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you open the wrong door?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is a plastic model shop, Zakunee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to be cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you want to be something, you have to learn about it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's only one option if you want to learn about cuteness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The picture in your head is a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You won't reach your goal if your map is unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can picture it once you have built this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's Minami Kotori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:50.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kotori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't know about Love Live!, Zakunee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine was really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Magazines, animes and movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They also performed at the Tokyo Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:01.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They also performed at Kouhaku, truly a legendary piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:07.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Otonokizaka Gakuin was on the verge of consolidation due to a decrease in the number of applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:14.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In order to increase the number of applicants, the students of \NOtonokizaka Gakuin voluntarily formed a 9-member School Idol, μ's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Minami Kotori is one of the members of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Her dream is to study fashion in the future, and she is in charge of the group's wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:26.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have any self-confidence, so in order to change that, she worked part-time at a maid cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:31.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She immediately became famous after she sang during an event,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:34.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,people call her the legendary maid Minalinsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:38.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She wants to have confidence in herself, that alone makes me want to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:44.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Teach me all about cuteness, Kotori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Open the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:54.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Grotesque.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:58.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as "cute" from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Quickly let all the parts out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Kotori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:14.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This looks so real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that it's going to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:21.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The striking blush on the cheeks is created by a technique called layered injection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:26.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The shining eyes have rounded iris edges to reproduce the blurring effect found in the original work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kotori-chan doesn't have any rough edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No rough edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's correct, Zakunee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:03.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Someone who doesn't get excited by the softness of the 3 layered lace won't be a cute person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Minami Kotori, give...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:29.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do anything to achieve cuteness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're free to do anything with plastic model and to achieve cuteness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cuteness is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:10.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's in the parts that are hard to see that cuteness resides in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:34.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The protagonist that is late to the party, Big Stone Victory Magnum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Big stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:48.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Being cute is your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Being cute is your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Last one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:27.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:43.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Minami Kotori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:47.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome to world of cuteness, Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did your heart flutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:52.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:57.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The more parts that I assembled, the amount of cuteness was also increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You won't be cute in just one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:08.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that I can be cute immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:10.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When you quickly become something,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,you will be bored with it as quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:15.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to add it day-by-day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kotori-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can be cute, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:26.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Big Stone Investigation HQ]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Department 3 Lunch Search Party]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:32.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Please let me treat the two of you to lunch today]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:39.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, it starts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:43.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:47.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:49.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:50.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:51.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:52.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:53.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:54.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:21:59.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:00.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:03.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did you revert back to your old self?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It seemed like you were about to come up with an aggressive project...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you have the time to worry about someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:09.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't revert back to my old self, Asai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:10.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:11.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't see that I added something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:12.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:14.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the way that you looked yesterday was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:16.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:22.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that you also look good today, Komukai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:27.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:28.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:31.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He said that I look good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:33.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,